<p><b>Dupont's lark</b> (<i>Chersophilus duponti</i>) is the only <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lark" title="Lark">lark</a> in the genus <i>Chersophilus</i>.</p>
<p></p>
<div id="toc" class="toc">
